# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __aenter__, __aexit__, __await__ across all 6 decimal subjects
#
# 6 classes x 3 methods = 18 rows.
# All eighteen values are false; no decimal class implements the async context
# manager or awaitable protocols in its own __dict__.
# decimal.Decimal is a numeric type defining many arithmetic operators
# but not the async context manager or awaitable protocol. Context is a
# precision/rounding configuration object; the exception subclasses are
# error types. None define __aenter__, __aexit__, or __await__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

